      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>When shopping, it can be all too easy to feel as if you're being taken for a fool, handing over a deck of bills for a scrap of black fabric with two buttons. These days, though, designers are making it easier for shoppers to deceive rather than be deceived, colluding with stores to create lower-priced lines. Below, eight pieces that can help you say -- silently -- April Fool.</p>
